  - API architecture, authentication, device groups, security policies, rate limiting, automation
- `.claude/research/2026-01-03-161615-panorama-commit-ops-targeted/` - Commit operations targeted research (1 file, 55KB)
  - Mandatory two-step workflow, job monitoring, error handling, rollback procedures
- `.claude/research/2026-01-03-165242-panorama-api-complete/` - Complete API endpoint reference (9 files, 160KB+)
